Package: igraphr
Type: Package
Title: Adds common graph operations to R igraph that makes graph manipulation via igraph simpler and easier to do. 
Version: 0.1
Author: Robert Ness
Description: igraphr creates higher level graph operations build upon the basic graph data 
             structure and graph operations found in igraph.  igraphr is useful to anyone 
             who likes using igraph as their primary tool for working with graph data 
             structures.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 2.14)
Imports: igraph (>= 0.7.1),
         bnlearn
Suggests: knitr,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
